Consumers can skip the market and buy fresh and un-processed grocery from the houses of their local crop/meat farmers, gardeners, fishers, etcetera. REGULATIONS: • Stakes will be finalized at the end of the Bounty Program. • Tokens will be awarded 2 weeks after the ICO ended. • We reserve the rights to cancel any of the campaigns base on the number of participants. • We reserve the right to disqualify your entries from any campaigns if:   1. You are not practicing honest conduct or spamming forums.   2. We might need to refuse you from participating in any of our Bounty Campaigns regardless of reason.   3. You must take action reaching the Bounty Manager for any issues within bounty week or we will not take fault for stakes lost.   4. Your entry does not meet the minimum requirements for that bounty week, you will not receive any stake in that current week. But you still have a chance to participate in the next bounty week   5. Spamming, cheating and having many accounts are strictly forbidden. We will completely remove you from all and any campaigns if found responsible under our management.    https://image.ibb.co/cokbWT/signature_camp_feedchain.png THIS CAMPAIGN WAS CANCELLED!!   https://image.ibb.co/h0Ydd8/article_camp_feedchain.png Submit your entries here: https://goo.gl/forms/gN9op8cbQAIGi0Z12 Participation Sheets: https://goo.gl/4Luaa5  Token Allocation: 20% allocation - 672 ETH worth of tokens per Article = 50 Stakes 1st 1000 claps = 20 Stakes per succeeding 2000 claps = 40 Stakes  Rules: 1. The article must be of high quality and proofread. 2. The article must be posted on Medium. 3. The content must be unique not just copy pasting from our ANN or Bounty content. 4. The article must be published publicly otherwise it would be rejected. 7. Participants must have at least 2000 followers to participate. 8. The article should contain not less than 500 words. 9. Twitter accounts with less than declared followers is an invalid entry. 4. We have the right to invalidate entries if a Bounty Hunter duplicated its entry even on different bounty weeks. 5.
